            <title>[SPARK-13482] `spark.storage.memoryMapThreshold` has two kind of the value.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-13482</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;`spark.storage.memoryMapThreshold` has two kind of the value, one is 2*1024*1024 as integer and the other one is &apos;2m&apos; as string.&lt;br/&gt;
